1.title: Ed Sheeran

episode of.title: Rolf and Willie's Machine of Awesomeness (TV Series 2017–2018)

1.plot: Ed Sheeran gets a surprise visit from Toonstar animated German Scientists Rolf and Willie as they quest to find out what makes the human voice so beautiful. To their surprise, Rolf and Willie wind up having to take the stage for Ed Sheeran and sing his hit song "The Shape of You". They wind up putting a little twist on the popular song using their love of science.

2.title: Star Wars

episode of.title: Rolf and Willie's Machine of Awesomeness (TV Series 2017–2018)

2.plot: Rolf and Willie meet their heroes from Star Wars: Yoga and Dunkle Vader (who may or not resemble Yoda and Darth Vader). Rolf and Willie learn to use the force and lessons about bringing their Star Wars friends together using donuts of all things.

3.title: Pizza

episode of.title: Rolf and Willie's Machine of Awesomeness (TV Series 2017–2018)

3.plot: Rolf and Willie get Pizza from its birthplace: Italy. Pizza can be delicious, especially when you get it in Sicily, Italy. But be careful when you go there, you might run into a godfather of a mafia town who owns a pizzeria and doesn't like when you insult his pizza.

4.title: Cristiano Ronaldo & Soccer

episode of.title: Rolf and Willie's Machine of Awesomeness (TV Series 2017–2018)

4.plot: Rolf and Willie visit the Fifa Soccer (Futbol) World Cup Final and meet Rolf's hero Cristiano Ronaldo. With the rivalry between the Portugal and German national teams, everything is riding on Cristiano's penalty kick.

5.title: Was Camelot Real?

episode of.title: Rolf and Willie's Machine of Awesomeness (TV Series 2017–2018)

5.plot: Rolf and Willie Camelot and fulfill their dreams of becoming a King and Court Jester. The famed King Arthur also faces the evil Draconus to ensure the safety of Camelot.
